# 📊 ServiceNow Data Model

The ServiceNow Data Model is the foundation of the platform. Every application in ServiceNow stores its information in tables. Each table contains records, and each record consists of multiple fields.

Understanding the Data Model is essential because almost every ServiceNow application is built using tables, records, and fields.

